## Important Notes

⚠️ **Project Structure**: This project does NOT use a `src/` folder - all directories are at the root level.

⚠️ **Backend**: This project uses **Convex** for backend operations, not Next.js Server Actions. Server-side logic is in `convex/_serverActions/`.

⚠️ **State Management**: Zustand stores are located in `stores/` at the root level, not `src/store/`.

⚠️ **Utilities**: Global utilities are in `lib/` at the root level, not `src/utils/`.
